{"tid":2225011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉國謙：家屬現階段不可能探望12人","createTime":"2020-10-01T03:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T04:49:33.000Z","uid":49776,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86a751eb997c708a33be0a2ed21abffe950db754","tid":2225011,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"12名港人涉嫌偷渡案，深圳鹽田區人民檢察院批准逮捕12人，其中兩人涉嫌組織他人偷越邊境罪，其餘10人涉嫌偷越邊境罪。其中最少一人申請取保候審被拒。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、港區人大代表葉國謙表示，以他了解，家屬現階段不可能探望12人，要在12人被判刑、或被無罪釋放後，雙方才可見面，又提到審訊期間可能有機會見到他們。他指，現時只有12人聘用的律師才可以與他們接觸。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有關台灣殺人案死者潘曉穎的母親批評民建聯未有再跟進事件，葉國謙表示，民建聯一直有與對方接觸，若潘太有需要，他本人亦願意提供協助。他指，現時特區政府不能在沒有法律基礎下將涉案的陳同佳引渡到台灣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552589-20201001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552589-20201001.htm&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w10BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=0ab1ec69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552589-20201001.htm&h=1e692f2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552589-20201001.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c7d30f06018fb919b600d73ef592a9f41fa8caa7","tid":2225011,"uid":284699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:00:20.000Z","msg":"陽光司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecda2676f2d4ea07799b8c38f49ff2081f20ad0","tid":2225011,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">黑警見字死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"449b6936e5eaefc9bb88f1934fde9a36d3bcc45c","tid":2225011,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 點解可以唔俾家屬見"},{"pid":"b4b63d29bb505c828302607a288508ee95fb549d","tid":2225011,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">聘乜撚用呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2d3bc8cf8fceb8df6cf679bcfd88b47b1c462316","tid":2225011,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c1e8d9555e6358919d19665b6500565fba57d3","tid":2225011,"uid":46275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"支那特色的陽光司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}